### ===================================================================
### PHASE 3: RUN INITIAL APPOINTMENT BOOKINGS
### ===================================================================

### Book Initial Stream Appointment (10:00 - 10:15)
# @name initialStreamAppointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointment
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "doctorId": "{{streamDocId}}",
  "date": "{{testDate}}",
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "10:15"
}

### Capture Stream Appt ID
@streamApptId = {{initialStreamAppointment.response.body.id}}


### Book Initial Wave Appointment (11:00 - 12:00)
# @name initialWaveAppointment
POST {{baseUrl}}/appointment
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "doctorId": "{{waveDocId}}",
  "date": "{{testDate}}",
  "startTime": "11:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}

### Capture Wave Appt ID
@waveApptId = {{initialWaveAppointment.response.body.id}}


---

### ===================================================================
### PHASE 4: RESCHEDULING & EDGE CASE TESTING
### ===================================================================

### ─── CASE A: STREAM RESCHEDULE (EXPECTED TO PASS) ───
### Shifts the active 10:00 AM slot to the open 10:15 AM slot.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/appointment/{{streamApptId}}/reschedule
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "doctorId": "{{streamDocId}}",
  "date": "{{testDate}}",
  "startTime": "10:15",
  "endTime": "10:30"
}


### ─── CASE B: STREAM RESCHEDULE (EXPECTED TO GRACEFULLY FAIL) ───
### Targets a historical date window to violate the past-time constraint.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/appointment/{{streamApptId}}/reschedule
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "doctorId": "{{streamDocId}}",
  "date": "2021-05-12",
  "startTime": "10:00",
  "endTime": "10:15"
}


### ─── CASE C: WAVE RESCHEDULE (EXPECTED TO PASS) ───
### Shifts out of the filled 11:00 AM wave window into the open 12:00 PM wave window.
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/appointment/{{waveApptId}}/reschedule
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "doctorId": "{{waveDocId}}",
  "date": "{{testDate}}",
  "startTime": "12:00",
  "endTime": "13:00"
}


### ─── CASE D: WAVE RESCHEDULE (EXPECTED TO GRACEFULLY FAIL) ───
### Tries to shift back into the 11:00 AM wave block which hit its capacity ceiling (maxWaveCapacity: 1).
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/appointment/{{waveApptId}}/reschedule
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "doctorId": "{{waveDocId}}",
  "date": "{{testDate}}",
  "startTime": "11:00",
  "endTime": "12:00"
}